_sText:
This map features:

- Anti-CP (no saving inside the level) Prefab here: [http://css.gamebanana.com/prefabs/6553](http://css.gamebanana.com/prefabs/6553 "http://css.gamebanana.com/prefabs/6553")

- Skillbased climbing

- LJ-Section up to 279

- Made for 10 and 100 aa

- Custom radar

- 5 soundscapes

It was made for 10 and 100 aa.
I tried to give the map a realistic looking and used some custom models and a lot of custom textures and decals. Thats why the filesize is higher then usual maps.

I hope you enjoy this map.

Dotty
